#: ../../source/docs/ops/diagnostic-tools/proxy-cmd/index.rst:234
msgid ""
"From the above summary you can see that every sidecar has a listener "
"bound to ``0.0.0.0:15001`` which is where IP tables routes all inbound "
"and outbound pod traffic to. This listener has ``useOriginalDst`` set to "
"true which means it hands the request over to the listener that best "
